:::Tigerhawk/Airazor:::

::Just a second ago they had seen Bluestreak propose to Andromeda.  They were 
amazed at how much they loved each other.  Pretty soon, ideas were forming in 
there own heads::
Tigerhawk: Remember what i said when we were abducted?
Airazor: Yes, you said: "Wherever we go my spark will find yours"
Tigerhawk: you know i meant that.
Airazor: I hope we never get separated again.
Tigerhawk: the feelings mutual.
::they lean over toward each other and kiss, as if they had just fallen in 
love::
